          0,
          ", Barrett this weekend appeared with Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell, R-Ky., at a celebration of a University of Louisville facility he named after himself. After being introduced by the most partisan Senate leader in American history, Barrett declared that the Supreme Court — which now includes "
