      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "This propaganda campaign has worked — even as the court exacerbates the climate crisis, restricts abortion rights, tramples voting rights and issues ever-more-extreme rulings helping corporations crush workers, "
